  "short_description": "Hero Planter is a new game experience in the farm simulation genre. Forget about that quiet corner in the back yard! In the dark dungeons, alone with cunning pests you will have to make every effort to grow crops and stay alive. One hero, one life, 100 unpredictable floors!",
